-- Brazil Extends Tax Cuts on Consumer Goods to Revive Economy
-- B y   A r n a l d o   G a l v a o
-- 2012-08-29T20:07:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-29/brazil-extends-tax-cuts-on-consumer-goods-to-revive-economy.html
Brazil is extending tax cuts on the
purchase of several consumer goods that were set to expire this
month, Finance Minsiter  Guido Mantega  said.  Tax cuts on the purchase of washing machines, furniture,
stoves, refrigerators and other home appliances will be extended
until Dec. 31, Mantega told reporters in Brasilia  To contact the reporter on this story:
